Package: basalt
Type: Package
Title: Live Ontology from a Markdown Vault
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Troy", "Hernandez", role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "troy@cornball.ai",
    comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0005-4248-604X"))
Description: Maintains a live ontology derived from a markdown vault with
    'YAML' frontmatter and typed links. Parses markdown files into a TSV
    index, supports graph traversal queries, suggests typed relations from
    untyped links, and emits OBO format snapshots.
